In Grafana we can create various kinds of dashboards as per our need

Click on new --> New dashboard --> Click on Add Visalization --> Select Data source

Add below query one by one in metric field --> click on run query --> change panel name --> change form time services to stat

click on Save dashboard


The below query will fetch the number of inactive plugins
jenkins_plugins_inactive{}

Click Add --> visualization --> again add the metric.


The below query will fetch the number of failed plugins
jenkins_plugins_failed{}

 The below query will fetch the number of plugins which required the update
jenkins_plugins_withUpdate{}

jenkins_job_count_value

Last build duration

default_jenkins_builds_last_build_duration_milliseconds

